4 (b) Except as provided in subsection (c), (d), or (e) of this section, during a regular
5 session of the General Assembly an official described in subsection (a) of this section, or a
6 person acting on behalf of the official, may not, as to a candidate for federal, State, or local
7 office[,] or a [campaign finance entity of the candidate or any other campaign finance entity
8 organized under this title and operated in coordination with a candidate] POLITICAL
